17
00:01:03,539 --> 00:01:08,759
Now, this question comes up when we talk
about LLMs in a multi-repo microservices

18
00:01:09,259 --> 00:01:15,249
kind of systems, where we like to leverage
AI to do more than just coding a specific

19
00:01:15,249 --> 00:01:18,439
feature in a specific repo, right?

20
00:01:18,919 --> 00:01:22,739
And we would like to use AI to help
