49
00:03:32,710 --> 00:03:38,310
We know that humans are historically bad
at documenting code, and on the other

50
00:03:38,310 --> 00:03:44,390
hand, AI is hungry for such documentation
in order to operate effectively So while

51
00:03:44,390 --> 00:03:51,160
the problem isn't inherent to AI, AIs
