405
00:29:17,179 --> 00:29:24,579
And the demand for, accurate system-level
context by AIs and the drive to

406
00:29:24,579 --> 00:29:31,799
have AI tackle more complicated
problems autonomously, right?

407
00:29:32,219 --> 00:29:36,469
Coupled with the LLM's ability to follow
