00:30:13,399 --> 00:30:16,139
understanding as well and check ourselves.

418
00:30:16,829 --> 00:30:20,319
Just the mere fact that it's written
down and it's up-to-date and correct

419
00:30:20,819 --> 00:30:26,839
gives us a lot of benefit and helps
our understanding Now, so far, we

